    • Constructor Detail

      • ModularityDetection

        public ModularityDetection(LinkedList<KeyWord> partKeywords,
                   double[][] correlations,
                   float startDay,
                   float endDay,
                   int window_,
                   String nwtFolder_)
                    throws Exception
        Running the modularity detection of each window : - instantiate the structure by adding the nodes then the edges (just we add to the network the nodes that have non zero values as correlation) -
        Parameters:
        partKeywords - the remaining significant keywords, in a List of 'KeyWord', after filtering with theta1
        correlations - correlation matrix of the keywords
        startDay - index of the first signal of the treated window
        endDay - indes of the end signal of the treated window
        window_ - index of the window to be run
        nwtFolder_ - folder containing nwt files
        Throws:
        Exception
